OL,6,F"So if there is an emergency at a
OL,7,Ftrain station, the fact that anyone
OL,8,Fwithin the community could potentially
OL,9,Fsign to a deaf member of society.
OL,11,F"I think it's really important. It's
OL,12,Fimportant to not be a second-class
OL,13,Fcitizen, it's about being a first-
OL,14,Fclass citizen."
OL,16,FStarring opposite Nadia is John
OL,17,FHollingworth, who's appeared in the
OL,18,Ffilm Napoleon (2023) and hit TV series
OL,19,FMr Bates vs The Post Office.
