OL,6,FHe takes on the role of Antony and
OL,7,Fbelieves their unique way of telling
OL,8,Fthis story, which includes the whole
OL,9,Fthing being captioned and displayed on
OL,10,Fmonitors, will actually ease
OL,11,Funderstanding.
OL,13,FHe says: "I think it's helpful for us
OL,14,Fand the audience. Sometimes
OL,15,FShakespeare can be quite difficult,
OL,16,Fpeople cannot be quite sure what they
OL,17,Fare saying."
